'''艾兰·库尔迪'''（{{lang-en|Alan Kurdi}}、{{lang-ku|Alan Kurdî}}，最初报道为Aylan Kurdi）<ref>{{cite web|title=Tima Kurdi is comforted by friend|url=http://news.yahoo.com/photos/tima-kurdi-comforted-friend-hoba-said-she-overcome-photo-180224731.html|website=雅虎新闻|accessdate=2015-09-05|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303213645/http://news.yahoo.com/photos/tima-kurdi-comforted-friend-hoba-said-she-overcome-photo-180224731.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Canada denies Alan Kurdi's family applied for asylum" />是一名[[敘利亞|敘利亞]]籍[[庫德族|庫德族]]三歲儿童。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/11841802/eu-migrant-crisis-refugee-boys-aylan-galip-kurdi.html|title=Aylan and Galip Kurdi: Everything we know about drowned Syrian refugee boys|publisher=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]|date=2015-09-03|access-date=2017-03-30|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125002705/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/11841802/eu-migrant-crisis-refugee-boys-aylan-galip-kurdi.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他于2015年9月2日在[[地中海|地中海]]溺亡后，他的照片成为全球新闻的头条。他和他的家人是在[[歐洲移民危機|欧洲难民危机]]（见[[欧洲移民危机年表|年表]]）中试图到达欧洲的叙利亚难民。他遗体的照片由土耳其[[记者|记者]][[尼魯佛·迪米爾|尼魯佛·迪米爾]]拍摄，并迅速在全球蔓延，促使国际反应。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/09/03/europe/migration-crisis-aylan-kurdi-turkey-canada/|title=Syrian toddler's dad: 'Everything I was dreaming of is gone'|publisher=CNN|date=2015-09-03|access-date=2017-03-30|archive-date=2021-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210427194337/https://edition.cnn.com/2015/09/03/europe/migration-crisis-aylan-kurdi-turkey-canada|dead-url=no}}</ref>因为据说库尔迪的家人一直试图前往[[加拿大|加拿大]]，他的死亡和更广泛的难民危机立即成为[[2015年加拿大联邦大选|2015年加拿大联邦大选]]的一个议题。

==个人经历==
库迪被认为于2012年或2013年出生在[[叙利亚|叙利亚]][[艾因阿拉伯|艾因阿拉伯]]。<ref name="new life"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/world/they-were-all-dead-abdullah-kurdi-describes-losing-his-family-at-sea-1.2546299|title='They were all dead: Abdullah Kurdi describes losing his family at sea'|publisher=[[CTV新闻|CTV新闻]]|date=2015-09-03|access-date=2017-03-30|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208063650/https://www.ctvnews.ca/world/they-were-all-dead-abdullah-kurdi-describes-losing-his-family-at-sea-1.2546299|dead-url=no}}</ref>一名叙利亚记者声称，他的姓是Shenu；在[[土耳其|土耳其]]使用“Kurdi”作为姓氏则是因为他们家的种族背景。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/sep/03/father-drowned-boy-aylan-kurdi-return-syria|title=Father of drowned boy Aylan Kurdi plans to return to Syria|author=Jessica Elgot|work=卫报|accessdate=2015-11-12|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309015059/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/sep/03/father-drowned-boy-aylan-kurdi-return-syria|dead-url=no}}</ref>在叙利亚北部各城市之间搬家逃离内战和[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]之后，<ref name=Telegraph>{{cite news|last1=Rayner|first1=Gordon|author2=Squires, Nick|title='Let this be the last', says heartbroken father of Aylan and Galip Kurdi as he prepares to bury them|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/11842795/Let-this-be-the-last-says-heartbroken-father-of-Aylan-and-Galip-Kurdi-as-he-prepares-to-bury-them.html|accessdate=2015-09-05|work=telegraph.co.uk|date=2015-09-03|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131065047/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/11842795/Let-this-be-the-last-says-heartbroken-father-of-Aylan-and-Galip-Kurdi-as-he-prepares-to-bury-them.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他家定居在土耳其。<ref name=Guardian>{{cite news|last1=Smith|first1=Helena|title=Aylan Kurdi: friends and family fill in gaps behind harrowing images|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/sep/03/refugee-crisis-friends-and-family-fill-in-gaps-behind-harrowing-images|accessdate=2015-09-05|work=卫报网站|date=2015-09-03|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108131458/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/sep/03/refugee-crisis-friends-and-family-fill-in-gaps-behind-harrowing-images|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年初，他家返回[[艾因阿拉伯|艾因阿拉伯]]，然而因為[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]再次攻击艾因阿拉伯，他們在2015年6月返回[[土耳其|土耳其]]。他們曾經兩次計畫前往[[希腊|希腊]][[科斯島|科斯島]]，然而並未施行，库迪的父亲決定計畫第三次的旅程。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/image-of-syrian-boy-washed-up-on-beach-hits-hard-1441282847|title=Image of Drowned Syrian Boy Echoes Around World|author1=Joe Parkinson in Istanbul|author2=David George-Cosh in Toronto|date=2015-09-03|work=华尔街日报|access-date=2017-03-30|archive-date=2021-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222120110/https://www.wsj.com/articles/image-of-syrian-boy-washed-up-on-beach-hits-hard-1441282847|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Canada denies Alan Kurdi's family applied for asylum" />

[[File:Alan_kurdi_smiling_playground.jpg|thumb]]

库尔迪的家人希望通过其在[[加拿大|加拿大]][[温哥华|温哥华]]的姑妈申请难民赞助后前往团聚，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2015/11/28/457697276/relatives-of-drowned-syrian-boy-will-move-to-canada|publisher=[[NPR|NPR]]|accessdate=2015-11-29|date=2015-11-28|last=Chappell|first=Bill|title=Relatives of Drowned Syrian Boy Will Move to Canada|archive-date=2020-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105110317/https://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2015/11/28/457697276/relatives-of-drowned-syrian-boy-will-move-to-canada|dead-url=no}}</ref>但[[加拿大公民及移民部|加拿大公民及移民部]]拒绝了他们的要求，部分原因是[[土耳其|土耳其]]当局拒绝其出境签证。<ref name="Death of Syrian toddler throws global spotlight onto refugees crisis">{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/world/europe/la-fg-syria-refugee-toddler-drowned-20150903-story.html|title=Death of Syrian toddler throws global spotlight onto refugees crisis|publisher=[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]|date=2015-09-03|access-date=2017-03-30|archive-date=2021-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210505192249/https://www.latimes.com/world/europe/la-fg-syria-refugee-toddler-drowned-20150903-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>據該部門稱，艾兰·库尔迪的父亲阿卜杜拉·库尔迪的兄弟穆罕默德的申请因不完整而被拒绝，并没有收到阿卜杜拉·库尔迪的申请。<ref name="Canada denies Alan Kurdi's family applied for asylum">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-34142695|title=Canada denies Alan Kurdi's family applied for asylum|publisher=BBC|date=2015-09-03|accessdate=2015-09-12|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308144358/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-34142695|dead-url=no}}</ref>阿卜杜拉·库尔迪说，[[加拿大政府|加拿大政府]]拒绝了他的庇护申请，他们应该为悲剧负责。<ref name="The Canadian Press">{{cite news|last1=The Canadian Press|url=http://www.ottawacommunitynews.com/news-story/5837017-abdullah-kurdi-faces-smuggling-allegations/|title=Abdullah Kurdi faces smuggling allegations|work=渥太华社区新闻|date=2015-09-11|accessdate=2015-09-13|archive-date=2017-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170324094956/http://www.ottawacommunitynews.com/news-story/5837017-abdullah-kurdi-faces-smuggling-allegations/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

加拿大[[新民主党_(加拿大)|新民主党]]（NDP）国会议员芬·唐纳利告诉媒体，該年早些时候他已经将库尔地家的文件递交移民、難民及公民部部长{{link-en|克里斯·亚历山大 (政治人物)|Chris Alexander (politician)|克里斯·亚历山大}}，但该申请在6月被拒绝，因为它是不完整的。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/news/canada/drowned-boys-family-sought-refuge-in-canada| title=Alan Kurdi drowned off the shores of Turkey. His family was trying to reach Canada|publisher=[[全国邮报|全国邮报]]|date=2015-09-03}}</ref>库尔迪家试图通过私人赞助计划进入加拿大，由五人组成的团体也可以赞助个人或家庭。他们必须证明他们可以提供大约27,000加元来支助四口难民的家庭。根据多伦多难民安置小组的“叙利亚生命线”项目经理亚历山德拉·科蒂克的说法，该计划要求前来加拿大的人首先被土耳其政府宣布为难民。而她认为这往往是一个困难甚至不可能实现的条件。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/09/04/world/americas/aylan-kurdis-death-raises-resonates-in-canadian-election-campaign.html?_r=0|title=Aylan Kurdi’s Death Resonates in Canadian Election Campaign|publisher=纽约时报|date=2015-09-03|accessdate=2017-03-30|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104092618/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/09/04/world/americas/aylan-kurdis-death-raises-resonates-in-canadian-election-campaign.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 出海遇难 ==
2015年9月2日凌晨，库尔迪和他的家人登上了一个小塑料或橡胶[[充气船|充气船]]，<ref name="deseretnews">{{cite news |url=http://www.deseretnews.com/article/765679302/Migrants-mass-in-Turkey-to-take-shortest-route-to-Europe.html?pg=all |title=Migrants mass in Turkey to take shortest route to Europe |publisher=德述里新闻报 |date=2015-08-16 |accessdate=2015-09-05 |archive-date=2017-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107112511/https://www.deseretnews.com/article/765679302/Migrants-mass-in-Turkey-to-take-shortest-route-to-Europe.html?pg=all |dead-url=no }}</ref>倾覆发生在离开土耳其[[博德鲁姆|博德鲁姆]]五分钟后。船只荷载八人，但船上实际有十六人。他们试图到达距离博德鲁姆大约30分钟({{convert|4|km|mi|frac=2|abbr=off|disp=or}})希腊[[科斯岛|科斯岛]]。库尔迪的父亲说：“我们没有[[救生衣|救生衣]]”，<ref name=spotlight>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/world/europe/la-fg-syria-refugee-toddler-drowned-20150903-story.html|title=Death of Syrian toddler throws global spotlight onto refugees crisis|author=洛杉矶时报|date=2015-09-03|work=latimes.com|accessdate=2015-11-12|archive-date=2021-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210505192249/https://www.latimes.com/world/europe/la-fg-syria-refugee-toddler-drowned-20150903-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>但也说他们穿着救生衣，但救生衣“都是假的”。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Timmons|first1=Heather|title=The father of Syrian toddler Aylan Kurdi on the boat ride that killed his family|url=http://qz.com/495211/the-life-jackets-we-were-wearing-were-all-fake-the-father-of-syrian-toddler-aylan-kurdi-on-the-boat-ride-that-killed-his-family/|accessdate=2015-09-09|work=qz.com|date=2015-09-04|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227052538/https://qz.com/495211/the-life-jackets-we-were-wearing-were-all-fake-the-father-of-syrian-toddler-aylan-kurdi-on-the-boat-ride-that-killed-his-family/|dead-url=no}}</ref>有人相信他们穿着[[救生衣|救生衣]]，但救生衣是无效的。<ref name="new life">{{cite news|last1=Hopper|first1=Tristin|title=The sad odyssey of Alan Kurdi and his family: Their search for new life ended in death|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/news/the-sad-odyssey-of-alan-kurdi-and-his-family|accessdate=2015-09-11|work=news.nationalpost.com|date=2015-09-03}}</ref>

后来叙利亚电台报道，库尔迪的家人为他们在船上的四个位置支付了5,860美元，尽管船只有约五[[米_(单位)|米]]长，但却有十二名乘客。艾兰·库尔迪的母亲也在旅行的团体中，尽管她害怕海。<ref name="Not Apply"/>媞玛·库尔迪，阿兰·库尔迪的姨妈，劝她姐姐不要去。船上的人在深夜通过一个孤立的海滩逃避土耳其海岸警卫队。<ref name="new life"/>

上午5时左右，当局接到船只倾覆和遺體漂上岸的紧急电话后，开始进行调查。<ref>{{cite news |title=Aylan bebeği taşıyan Mehmet Çıplak konuştu |url=http://www.haberturk.com/gundem/haber/1124990-aylan-bebegi-tasiyan-mehmet-ciplak-konustu |publisher=[[新闻土耳其|新闻土耳其]]（Haberturk） |date=2015-09-06 |accessdate=2015-09-08 |archive-date=2020-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807120130/https://www.haberturk.com/gundem/haber/1124990-aylan-bebegi-tasiyan-mehmet-ciplak-konustu |dead-url=no }}</ref>库尔迪的遺體和另一个孩子被两个当地人在上午6:30左右发现。<ref name="roberts-dailymail">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3220992/Their-eyes-open-closed-softly-Turkish-barman-body-toddler-Aylan-Kurdi-beach-relives-horror.html|title=Turkish barman who found body of migrant toddler Aylan Kurdi on beach relives horror|date=2015-09-03|work=邮报在线|accessdate=2015-11-12|archive-date=2019-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190406190453/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3220992/Their-eyes-open-closed-softly-Turkish-barman-body-toddler-Aylan-Kurdi-beach-relives-horror.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>这两个人把遺體从水中移动到海滩上干燥的地方。<ref name="roberts-dailymail"/>后来，库尔迪被土耳其摄影记者拍摄到趴在水边的照片。<ref name="roberts-dailymail" /><ref name=Morningmix>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/09/03/a-desperate-refugee-family-a-capsized-boat-and-3-year-old-dead-on-a-beach-in-turkey/|title=Aylan’s story: How desperation left a 3-year-old boy washed up on a Turkish beach|author=Justin Wm. Moyer|date=2015-09-03|work=华盛顿邮报|accessdate=2015-11-12|archive-date=2021-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210235406/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/09/03/a-desperate-refugee-family-a-capsized-boat-and-3-year-old-dead-on-a-beach-in-turkey/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Echoes>{{cite web|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/image-of-syrian-boy-washed-up-on-beach-hits-hard-1441282847|title=Image of Drowned Syrian Boy Echoes Around World|author1=Joe Parkinson in Istanbul|author2=David George-Cosh in Toronto|date=2015-09-03|work=华尔街日报|accessdate=2015-11-12|archive-date=2021-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222120110/https://www.wsj.com/articles/image-of-syrian-boy-washed-up-on-beach-hits-hard-1441282847|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年9月3日，库尔迪与哥哥加利布和母亲蕾哈娜被送往艾因阿拉伯，<ref>{{cite web|title=Drowned migrant boy Alan Kurdi is buried in Syria|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-34150364|website=bbc.com|accessdate=2015-09-03|archive-date=2020-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221204845/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-34150364|dead-url=no}}</ref>第二天举行[[伊斯兰教葬礼|葬礼]]。如果可能的话，在24小时内埋葬死者是伊斯兰教的传统<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.msn.com/en-us/news/world/iraqi-familys-dream-of-europe-ends-in-terror-loss/ar-AAe7dV6?ocid=spartandhp|title=Iraqi family's dream of Europe ends in terror, loss|publisher=|accessdate=2015-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304090039/http://www.msn.com/en-us/news/world/iraqi-familys-dream-of-europe-ends-in-terror-loss/ar-AAe7dV6?ocid=spartandhp|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[科巴尼之戰|科巴尼之戰]]于2015年3月结束，2015年8月，<ref>{{cite news|title=Islamic State kills at least 145 civilians in Syria's Kobani|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-idUSKBN0P60UY20150626|work=路透社|date=2015-06-26|accessdate=2017-03-30|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124134758/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-idUSKBN0P60UY20150626|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Syria crisis: IS makes deadly return to Kobane - BBC News|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-33266399|work=BBC新闻|language=en|accessdate=2017-03-30|archive-date=2018-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181028185443/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-33266399|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]完全停止了对这座城市的袭击。<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-30991612 |title= Syrian Kurds 'drive Islamic State out of Kobane' |date= 2015-01-26 |accessdate= 2015-01-26 |publisher= BBC新闻 |archive-date= 2019-03-31 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190331053943/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-30991612 |dead-url= no }}</ref>

== 追究肇事者 ==
土耳其当局随后逮捕了四名与偷渡有关的人，虽然他们似乎是低階的中间人。<ref name=spotlight/>

艾兰·库尔迪的父亲阿卜杜拉·库尔迪在部分采访中表示，充气船因为引擎故障而变得不可控制，船长放弃了船只和其他人。 一些土耳其人声称，在他第一次接受[[多安通讯社|多安通讯社]]的采访时，他给出了不同的事件描述；他还说，在两次尝试进入希腊[[科斯島|科斯島]]未果，他的家人用自己的方式找到船只。<ref name=dha>{{cite news|url=http://www.dha.com.tr/he-slipped-through-my-fingers-says-father-of-syrian-toddler-aylan-kurdi_1017517.html|title="He slipped through my fingers" says father of Syrian toddler Aylan Kurdi|publisher=[[多安通讯社|多安通讯社]]|date=2015-09-03|accessdate=2015-09-27|archive-date=2015-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905191336/http://www.dha.com.tr/he-slipped-through-my-fingers-says-father-of-syrian-toddler-aylan-kurdi_1017517.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=nypost>{{cite news|url=http://nypost.com/2015/09/03/father-of-drowned-syrian-boys-says-overloaded-boat-flipped/|script-title=en:Anguished dad of drowned Syrian boys: ‘I realized they were all dead’|publisher=[[纽约邮报|纽约邮报]]|date=2015-09-03|accessdate=2015-09-27|archive-date=2020-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815135307/https://nypost.com/2015/09/03/father-of-drowned-syrian-boys-says-overloaded-boat-flipped/|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，阿卜杜拉從未證實接受多安通讯社的采访。

