== 各界反应 ==
库尔迪遺體的照片引起了国际上的愤慨。法国总统[[弗朗索瓦·奥朗德|弗朗索瓦·奥朗德]]在媒体上报道了库尔迪的照片后致电给土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安和一些欧洲国家领导人。他说，这张照片应该唤起世界各国对难民的责任。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailysabah.com/diplomacy/2015/09/03/french-president-calls-erdogan-over-images-of-drowned-syrian-boy-calls-for-common-eu-refugee-policy|title=French President calls Erdoğan over images of drowned Syrian boy, calls for common EU refugee policy|publisher=[[沙巴日报|沙巴日报]]|date=2015-09-03|access-date=2017-03-30|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126222847/https://www.dailysabah.com/diplomacy/2015/09/03/french-president-calls-erdogan-over-images-of-drowned-syrian-boy-calls-for-common-eu-refugee-policy|dead-url=no}}</ref>英国首相[[戴维·卡梅伦|戴维·卡梅伦]]表示，他看到庫爾迪的照片後非常感傷。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/aylan-kurdi-david-cameron-says-he-felt-deeply-moved-by-images-of-dead-syrian-boy-but-gives-no-details-of-plans-to-take-in-more-refugees-10484641.html|title=Aylan Kurdi: David Cameron says he felt 'deeply moved' by images of dead Syrian boy but gives no details of plans to take in more refugees|publisher=[[獨立報|獨立報]]|date=2015-09-03|accessdate=2017-03-30|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925165543/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/aylan-kurdi-david-cameron-says-he-felt-deeply-moved-by-images-of-dead-syrian-boy-but-gives-no-details-of-plans-to-take-in-more-refugees-10484641.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>爱尔兰总理[[恩达·肯尼|恩达·肯尼]]评论库尔迪照片和难民危机为“人类的灾难”，还认为照片“绝对的令人震惊”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.ie/irish-news/a-young-boy-washed-up-on-beach-like-driftwood-taoiseach-describes-migrant-crisis-as-human-catastrophe-31500065.html|title='A young boy... washed up on beach like driftwood' - Taoiseach describes migrant crisis as 'human catastrophe'|publisher=[[爱尔兰独立报|爱尔兰独立报]]|date=2015-09-03|access-date=2017-03-30|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809180214/https://www.independent.ie/irish-news/a-young-boy-washed-up-on-beach-like-driftwood-taoiseach-describes-migrant-crisis-as-human-catastrophe-31500065.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

这张照片被认为导致向慈善机构捐助用于帮助移民和难民的捐款激增，一个名叫{{link-en|移民离岸援助站|Migrant Offshore Aid Station}}的慈善机构，在照片出版后24小时接收的捐款增加了15倍。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Henley|first1=Jon|title=Britons rally to help people fleeing war and terror in Middle East|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2015/sep/03/britons-rally-to-help-people-fleeing-war-and-terror-in-middle-east|accessdate=2015-09-03|publisher=卫报|date=2015-09-03|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108113045/http://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2015/sep/03/britons-rally-to-help-people-fleeing-war-and-terror-in-middle-east|dead-url=no}}</ref>《每日邮报》在9月10日的一篇文章指出，令人伤心的库尔迪之死和相关图像“突显了全球移民危机可怕的人道成本”。<ref name=ISIS/>

