oy-did-not-apply-to-sponsor-family-in-canada-1.3214517|accessdate=2015-09-04|agency=CBC新闻|archive-date=2021-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506013731/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/aunt-of-alan-kurdi-drowned-syrian-boy-did-not-apply-to-sponsor-family-in-canada-1.3214517|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Canada denies Alan Kurdi's family applied for asylum" />-{zh-cn:托马斯·马尔凯;zh-hk:唐民凱}-后来替唐纳利辩护，说没有道歉的必要，因为这封信提到了两个家庭，并且他在党团会议表示“不可能骄傲地像芬·唐纳利一样有实力、有气节和努力工作”。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/election/mulcair-stands-behind-donnelly-after-kurdi-family-confusion-1.2558642 | title=Mulcair stands behind Donnelly, after Kurdi family confusi | publisher=[[CTV新闻|CTV新闻]] | date=2015-09-11 | accessdate=2015-09-11 | archive-date=2020-12-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212134426/https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/election/mulcair-stands-behind-donnelly-after-kurdi-family-confusion-1.2558642 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

